Our Location
Village on the Greens is a vibrant 55+ manufactured home community nestled on 50 beautifully maintained acres. With a focus on active living, our community offers a variety of amenities and activities designed to enhance your lifestyle. Conveniently located in Bradenton, Florida, Village on the Greens is just minutes from stunning Gulf Coast beaches, golf courses, and a variety of shopping and dining options, providing residents with the perfect balance of tranquility and nearby attractions.

Our Community
Village on the Greens is a close-knit 55+ community where residents enjoy an active, social lifestyle. Spanning 50 acres, our beautifully landscaped grounds feature a pool, clubhouse, and outdoor spaces perfect for gatherings. Our residents form lasting connections through events, activities, and shared interests. Located in Bradenton, Florida, the community thrives on its welcoming atmosphere, making it a great place to call home.

Amenities
Stay Engaged and Build Lasting Connections
At Village on the Greens, we are committed to enhancing the well-being of our 55+ community. Our thoughtfully designed amenities, including a refreshing pool, modern clubhouse, and outdoor recreation areas, provide endless opportunities for staying active and social. Whether you’re enjoying fitness activities or participating in community events, you’ll have plenty of chances to connect with new friends and create lasting memories in this vibrant, welcoming environment.
